<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="studio-n">studio <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'stjuːdiəʊ/    美 /'stuːdioʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(广播、电视的) 演播室；录音室；录制室：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Romeo and Juliet is being broadcast from our studio.
我们的演播室正在播放《罗密欧与朱丽叶》。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Musicians record their songs in a studio.
音乐家在录音棚录制歌曲。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(画家、雕刻家、摄影师等的) 工作室：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The artist is at his studio, painting.
画家正在他的画室里作画。</p></div></div>